 <SENTIMENT>Mixed</SENTIMENT>
 <VALUE>The staff working under Dr Yun was very nice and helpful. Dr Yun could frankly have better manners and a better temperament and be more engaging and interested in the patients needs. I realize he has a stressful and demanding job but I am taking this into consideration. I have worked with thousands of doctors and residents during my own career and I am empathetic to them and am capable tof overlooking things for that reason.</VALUE>
