 <VALUE>Please see previous comments as to why the fair rating. Dr Yun could communicate better and show more genuine concern. In the beginning of the consultation my sister told him she had heard great things about him and said she knew a handful of people he had operated on and that they were all extremely happy with their results. He didn't seem to appreciate the praise that much and just wanted to get on with whatever was necessary for him to say and be done with it. That's my take. I hope time and outcome changes my mind about my rating. I am really a people person and don't like awful conflict especially as I am waiting to have a major and stressful surgery.</VALUE>
 </RESPONSE>
